    ğŸ’¡ Best Practice: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
    âš ï¸  Issue: Header is missing entirely.

âœ…  X-Content-Type-Options    : OK
    â„¹ï¸  Prevents the browser from 'sniffing' the response type.
    ğŸ’¡ Best Practice: nosniff
